572
00:34:44,083 --> 00:34:45,625
Mumtaz's second husband.

573
00:34:45,708 --> 00:34:46,666
He's there as well.

574
00:34:46,791 --> 00:34:49,250
My blood pressure is rising.

575
00:34:49,333 --> 00:34:51,708
