Comb bald heads for life?

638
00:38:10,750 --> 00:38:13,166
We were born poor,
but we won't die poor.

639
00:38:13,291 --> 00:38:17,375
Listen, I've promised Manu
I'll get her to England.

640
00:38:19,000 --> 00:38:20,166
